00:00:06.220 --> 00:00:09.780
&gt;&gt; John Kelly: Wouldn't you like
to be reincarnated as a taste bud

00:00:09.780 --> 00:00:12.950
on Calvin Trillin's tongue?

00:00:12.950 --> 00:00:15.920
