of parking."

00:01:22.690 --> 00:01:26.800
I did not look to see if the
Melville entry in Wikipedia said,

00:01:26.800 --> 00:01:31.860
"It is unusual among novels for
exploring the subject of whales."

00:01:33.250 --> 00:01:37.860
Calvin Trillin started out as
a journalist at Time Magazine.

00:01:37.860 --> 00:01:41.190
His first piece is in The New
Yorker about desegregation

00:01:41.190 --> 00:01:45.770
at the University of Georgia
were published in 1963.

00:01:45.770 --> 00:01:49.930
