in its pages ever since.

00:01:49.930 --> 00:01:53.110
In the summer of 1990
prompted by the sound

00:01:53.110 --> 00:01:57.280
of John Sununu's last
name, he wrote the first

00:01:57.280 --> 00:01:59.590
of a series of short poems.

00:01:59.590 --> 00:02:03.870
