name would be worthy of parody now.

00:02:10.360 --> 00:02:12.390
That was in the nation
and he continues

00:02:12.390 --> 00:02:17.830
to skew our nations politics and
culture in verse on deadline.

00:02:17.830 --> 00:02:23.130 position:56%
