Thurber Prize for American Humor.

00:02:23.130 --> 00:02:28.300
He once said, "I actually think of
being funny as an odd turn of mind.

00:02:28.300 --> 00:02:30.410
Like a mild disability.

00:02:30.410 --> 00:02:34.850
